    "Other examples are the enhancement of a landslide early warning system introducing susceptibility-related areas based on catching autocorrelation of landslide locations with rainfall variables 101, and an approach to assessing the spatiotemporal variations of vegetation productivity based on the SAC indices, valuable for integrated ecosystem management 102.",
